steps.html_instructions: Take the ramp on the left onto I-10 W
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-10 W

Turn right onto US-377 N/US-83 N/N Main St
Continue to follow US-83 N

Turn left onto US-87 N/W Broadway St
Continue to follow US-87 N

Continue straight onto TX-163 N/US-87 N
Continue to follow US-87 N
Slight left onto US-87 BUS N/S Dallas Ave

Turn right onto TX-137 N/N Bryan Ave
Continue to follow TX-137 N

Turn left onto US-380 W/US-82 W/W Main St (signs for Plano)
Continue to follow US-380 W
Entering New Mexico

Turn right onto US-285 N/N Main St
Continue to follow US-285 N
Turn left onto the I-25 S/US-285 S ramp to Santa Fe
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
